---
title: Prosciutto-Wrapped Chicken Saltimbocca with Garlic-Sage Spinach & Burst Tomatoes
description: Our play on Roman-style Saltimbocca incorporates all the best parts of this famous dish: crispy prosciutto, herbaceous sage, and a rich, intensely flavorful sauce. We’ve nixed the tedious prep work to give you an elegant weeknight dinner ready in under 30 minutes.
